# App Features

This file documents all major user-facing features in the app. Update this file whenever new functionality is added.

## Authentication & Onboarding
- User sign up with email, password, and profile photo
- User sign in with email and password
- Onboarding flow for new users
- Profile photo upload during sign up

## User Profile
- View own profile
- View friend profiles
- Change profile picture
- Delete account
- Log out

## Friends System
- Friend code system for adding friends
- QR code generation for friend codes
- Share friend code via native share functionality
- Send friend invites using friend codes
- Accept incoming friend requests
- View friend list
- Remove friends
- Block friends
- View incoming friend requests

## Notifications
- Push notifications for friend-related activities
- Accept friend invite notifications

## Location Services
- Location tracking (native implementation available)

## Camera & Media
- Camera functionality for profile photos
- Photo upload and storage

## Navigation
- Tab-based navigation
- Modal navigation for add friend screen
- Profile page navigation
